Quel(le) decorator is used to create a property that can be set?
```python
class Circle:
    def __init__(self, radius):
        self._radius = radius
    @property
    def radius(self):
        return self._radius
    @radius.setter
    def radius(self, value):
        if value < 0:
            raise ValueError("Radius cannot be negative")
        self._radius = value
```
